          ITMAP DOES NOT WARRANT OR MAKE ANY REPRESENTATIONS REGARDING THE USE, VALIDITY, ACCURACY OR RELIABILITY OF THIS WEBSITE (ITMAP.COM) OR THE RESULTS OF THE USE OF THE WEBSITE. IN NO EVENT SHALL ITMAP BE LIABLE FOR ANY DAMAGES, INCLUDING THOSE ARISING AS A RESULT OF ITMAP'S NEGLIGENCE, WHETHER THOSE DAMAGES ARE DIRECT, CONSEQUENTIAL, INCIDENTAL, OR SPECIAL, FLOWING FROM YOUR USE OF OR INABILITY TO USE THE WEBSITE OR INFORMATION PROVIDED HEREWITH OR RESULTS OF THE WEBSITE.THE ULTIMATE RESPONSIBILITY FOR ACHIEVING THE RESULTS REMAINS WITH YOU.
        </p>
      </div>
</section>
